"opts=download] (MS Word 345 KB)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/use-case-herbarium-specimens.adoc:57
msgid ""
"Download xref:attachment$UC-HS-1-base-material.zip[UC-HS-1-base-material.zip,"
"opts=download]. (34.4 MB). There are 10 images. Two images per specimen for "
"a total of five specimens.  The herbarium sheets are in Spanish (data may "
"come to you in various means and in other languages than your own), but you "
"should be able to recognize the data contained in the fields on the labels. "
"Remember to use both images per record to compile the information."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
